      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; iterative convergence monitored via residual drop of 10^-5 as surrogate.",
      "rationale": "MRL 2 does not require formal iterative error quantification beyond residual monitoring. All simulations converged to 10^-5 residual. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2."
