      "rationale": "Fluid properties, pump geometry, and operating conditions sourced from FDA benchmark dataset and manufacturer drawings. Input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2; nominal values used throughout."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
