      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single FDA benchmark geometry used; sample variability not applicable to geometric validation case.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump is a single canonical geometry; no manufacturing variability exists in the benchmark dataset. Test-sample factor is not applicable for this validation activity at MRL 2."
